<item>
            <title>[AMQ-942] ActiveMQStreamMessage should support large text format in writeString.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-942</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I was wondering if ActiveMQStreamMessage should support large text messages also, since MapMessage is also able to support this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
